 and loans from shady dealers. Mourne's ex wife shows and threatens to tie Quark up in legal holding, if he doesn't cut her in on the profits.::Jared Johnson"],"imdbRating":7.6,"originalAirDate":"4 Feb. 1998","imdbURL":"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0708665/","plotOutline":"Mourn, dies in a shuttle crash, and Quark, now inherited all his debt and former dealings wanting to collect money from his now inherited mess with Mourn's former dealers and loans from shady dealers. Mourne's ex wife shows and threatens to tie Quark up in legal holding, if he doesn't cut her in on the profits."},{"title":"Far Beyond the Stars","episodeID":"0708538","plot":["Captain Sisko has a full sensory vision of himself as an under-appreciated science fiction magazine writer in 1950s America.::Kenneth Chisholm"],"imdbRating":8.8,"originalAirDate":"11 Feb. 1998","imdbURL":"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0708538/","plotOutline":null},{"title":"One Little Ship","episodeID":"0708572","plot":["A Dominion attack on the Defiant endangers Dax, Bashir and O'Brien aboard the runabout U.S.S. Rubicon as they enter an anomaly that shrinks them to a very minute size. Unfortunately, they were being held stable by the Defiant within a tractor beam, which was discontinued during the attack.::Moviedude1"],"imdbRating":7.6,"originalAirDate":"18 Feb. 1998","imdbURL":"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0708572/","plotOutline":"A Dominion attack on the Defiant endangers Dax, Bashir and O'Brien aboard the runabout U.S.S. Rubicon as they enter an anomaly that shrinks them to a very minute size. Unfortunately, they were being held stable by the Defiant within a tractor beam, which was discontinued during the attack."},{"title":"Honor Among Thieves","episodeID":"0708550","plot":["Chief O'Brien goes undercover to infiltrate an Orion crime ring.::Kenneth Chisholm"],"imdbRating":7.3,"originalAirDate":"25 Feb. 1998","imdbURL":"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0708550/","plotOutline":null},{"title":"Change of Heart","episodeID":"0708515",